{"tid":1641422,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"39歲男子遊印度後返港確診霍亂　今年首宗","createTime":"2019-10-09T10:30:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-09T10:43:27.000Z","uid":240362,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"a159338b0417c756a8525191fb1935db8bb377c5","tid":1641422,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T10:30:29.000Z","msg":"衞生署衞生防護中心今日(9日)表示，正調查一宗外地傳入的霍亂確診個案，涉及一名39歲男病人過往健康良好。他於9月10日至30日期間曾到印度，10月1日開始出現腹瀉，10月5日入住律敦治醫院接受隔離治療，10月8日轉往瑪嘉烈醫院繼續隔離治療，情況一直穩定。<br />\n他的糞便樣本經化驗後，今日證實含產生腸毒素的霍亂弧菌O1小川型。衞生防護中心正繼續調查個案。<br />\n衞生署衞生防護中心並再次呼籲市民，不論在香港或外遊時，保持良好個人、食物及環境衞生。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20191009/bkn-20191009181837951-1009_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20191009%2Fbkn-20191009181837951-1009_00822_001.html&d=B%2BAVUFxUUUF%2FouYpVm7lNqzbj60slk4H2lWqI%2F1XlBQ%3D&h=1a22e8f6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20191009/bkn-20191009181837951-1009_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"2fd51c68e31d78c36336d055dbf424281af6a20b","tid":1641422,"uid":271434,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T10:31:52.000Z","msg":"【行動核彈】隊㝝WeChat妙法！借警察報料熱線一齊將騰訊列美國制裁名單！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n詳情請閱：<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1641145\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1641145</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/chrsTee.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FchrsTee.jpg&h=60437086&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ddfcfd4a021c3a1df3ffc77b8757b198e287b716","tid":1641422,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2fd51c68e31d78c36336d055dbf424281af6a20b","tid":1641422,"uid":271434,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T10:31:52.000Z","msg":"【行動核彈】隊㝝WeChat妙法！借警察報料熱線一齊將騰訊列美國制裁名單！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n